701876f-a.title: Bronx: Story Avenue - Boynton Avenue
701876f-a.text:
Story Ave. (activity thereon), west from Boynton to Elder Aves.,
showing the thoroughfare being cut through by the W.P.A. Also shown is
EA general view westward across the salt meadows.
December 14, 1936.
Works Progress Admintstration.
Federal Art Project photo.
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.
